import React from 'react'
import {Lottie, Text, View} from '../../atoms'
import * as Notfound from '../../../assets/lottiefiles/404.json'

const NotFound  = ({title}) => {

    return (
        <View direction="column" height="100vh">
            <View flexValue="1">
                <Lottie path={Notfound.default} width={600}/>
            </View>
            <View justify="center">
                <Text align="center" size="16" margin="0 100px 0 0">{title}</Text>
            </View>
        </View>
    )
}

export default NotFound
